## 终点{ #gist_endpoints } 
<!--DHIS2-SECTION-ID:gist_endpoints-->

`/gist` API 有 3 种端点：

* <code>/api/&lt;object-type><b>/gist</b></code>: paged list of all known and visible objects of the type (implicit `auto=S`)
